				\setlength{\oddsidemargin}{-69pt}
				\begin{document}$$\chi $$\end{document}. Imposing further dynamical assumptions, one is left with twelve models, whose properties are summarized in Table 3. The details of the models have been extensively explored in Ref. [15], so here we will simply recall their main features.
